2240 CALL "ZZPROM",".YE",X3$,Z0,X$,"","",0; ON Z0 GOTO 2250,2290,2260
2250 A$(1,8)=A1$(I,8); EXITTO 9900
2260 EXITTO 2320
2290 NEXT I
2300 X$=""
